        "created_at": "2021-07-09T23:33:35.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I just received an offer for some '18\u2019s and Lafon\u2019s Meursault Genevrieres was priced higher than Roulot\u2019s. This surprised me. I feel like it\u2019s almost always the opposite. Is Roulot\u2019s not Domaine\u2013he does not distinguish any more I know\u2013or is it a sign of a broader change?</p>",
